00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:43,880
books is probably going to be a much better use of your time. Even watching a foreign

55
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:48,800
film with subtitles is probably better than Duolingo. I will say though that Duolingo might

56
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:53,680
be useful as a supplementary tool alongside real studying, or maybe you're in a situation

57
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:57,680
where you learned a second language a while ago and just need a refresher. There's not

58
00:04:57,680 --> 00:05:02,720
much else to say about this topic, aside from some mildly funny memes about how the Duolingo

