74
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:35,760
or a consonant cluster, if you will. So the entire sound is shifted.

75
00:06:35,760 --> 00:06:40,400
Squid becomes id-squay. And finally, some words start with vowels,

76
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:44,320
so you just add wey or yay at the end, like and-yay.

77
