87
00:07:21,440 --> 00:07:25,280
so it's still sort of objective. These languages are the easiest,

88
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:30,400
and take 23 to 24 weeks to learn. The easiest of all of these is apparently Spanish,

89
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:33,680
according to data from the language learning platform Basu.

90
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:37,360
Next, German is in a category of its own, taking 30 weeks.

91
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:42,160
