99
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:08,960
Mandarin is also what's known as a tonal language,

100
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:12,560
where the specific tone of your speech changes the meaning of a word.

101
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:16,960
We have a bit of that in English, like rising into nation when we ask questions.

102
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:20,880
For example, the word ma in Mandarin can mean mom, numb,

103
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:23,440
horse, or to curse, depending on your tone.

