720
00:46:52,640 --> 00:46:55,040
and has less than 200 words.

721
00:46:55,040 --> 00:46:57,280
To actually describe anything complicated,

722
00:46:57,280 --> 00:47:00,160
you need to break it down into much simpler terms.

723
00:47:00,160 --> 00:47:01,520
Sonia Lang wrote,

724
00:47:01,520 --> 00:47:05,520
If English is a thick novel, then Tokipona is a haiku.

725
00:47:05,520 --> 00:47:07,120
The reason this language was created

726
00:47:07,120 --> 00:47:09,440
and why it's used is also pretty interesting.

727
00:47:09,440 --> 00:47:11,520
It's almost a philosophical language.

728
00:47:11,520 --> 00:47:14,080
