857
00:53:16,240 --> 00:53:20,880
mostly because Schleyer refused to allow anyone other than himself to create new words.

858
00:53:20,880 --> 00:53:24,080
Loads of sub-languages were created, like Nalbino,

859
00:53:24,080 --> 00:53:29,600
Balta, Bopal, Speline, Dil, and Orba, but they were almost immediately forgotten.

860
00:53:29,600 --> 00:53:34,320
